channel.title: What are all the mod/admin commands?
channel.description: Well I'm in a bit of a mess up here when I make ppl mod/admin. They always say what are the mod commands and since I went to co owner right away I really wouldn't know...Also if I check in my client for some things that are supposed to be there, they are not there. My brother has made an awesome server off of the source allstar scape v2. Can someone tell me all the mod commands so I never need to answer that and just make a command for the commands? :D :confused:

item.title: What are all the mod/admin commands?
item.dc:creator: @Gh0stb4rr4g3 Gh0stb4rr4g3
item.description:
@Gh0stb4rr4g3 wrote:

Goto your client.java and search:

if (command.startsWith("eat")

If u can’t find it search for:

if (command.startsWith("rep"))

Than just scroll down there will be all commands you can use in ur server.

Hope this helped.
